#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/TG/tg_12f.rst:6 d54fef700fa94aa99eefe6851d1c73f1
msgid "`平头哥官方资料获取 <https://occ.t-head.cn/vendor/detail/download?id=3840454249402605568&vendorId=3706716635429273600&module=1#sticky>`__"
msgstr "`Get official T-Head documentation <https://occ.t-head.cn/vendor/detail/download?id=3840454249402605568&vendorId=3706716635429273600&module=1#sticky>`__"

#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/TG/tg_12f.rst:8 a733971203fb43deb0ef2862fa82f56c
msgid "TG-12F模块采用平头哥TG7100C芯片，TG7100C 是智能新一代高集成 Wi-Fi 和 BLE 组合芯片。无线子系统包含 2.4G 射频、Wi-Fi 802.11b/g/n 和 BLE 基带/MAC 设计。微控制器子系统包含一个低功耗 32 位 RISC CPU、高速缓存和存储器。电源管理单元提供灵活的设置实现低功耗模式，并支持多种安全功能。"
msgstr "The TG-12F module uses the T-Head TG7100C chip. TG7100C is a new-generation highly integrated smart Wi-Fi and BLE combo chip. The wireless subsystem includes 2.4G RF, Wi-Fi 802.11b/g/n, and BLE baseband/MAC designs. The microcontroller subsystem includes a low-power 32-bit RISC CPU, high-speed cache, and memory. The power management unit provides flexible settings to implement low-power modes and supports multiple security features."

#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/TG/tg_12f.rst:10 4f9d2f31ebc2436b9d46d78188280bbe
msgid "产品特性："
msgstr "Product features:"

#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/TG/tg_12f.rst:12 d00028bbfa284d47962d432dd425c1ac
msgid "802.11b/g/n，Wi-Fi+BLE5.0 Combo，支持 STA，Soft AP 和 Sniffer模式"
msgstr "802.11b/g/n, Wi-Fi + BLE5.0 Combo, supports STA, Soft AP, and Sniffer modes"

#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/TG/tg_12f.rst:13 fe9db1302ddc449f8ac7a920832c7799
msgid "采用开源自主可控 RISC-V CPU，1～160MHz 可调，276KB SRAM"
msgstr "Uses an open-source, independently controllable RISC-V CPU, adjustable from 1 to 160MHz, with 276KB SRAM"

#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/TG/tg_12f.rst:14 0266c8bee2484bef9c4a369c77c945aa
msgid "超快连接：冷启动快连仅 70ms"
msgstr "Ultra-fast connection: cold-start quick connection in only 70ms"

#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/TG/tg_12f.rst:15 1cbfbbe39b2f4c56b1b9325b5ddc1953
msgid "超远距离：最大发射功率 21dBm，灵敏度-98dBm，多穿透一堵墙。"
msgstr "Ultra-long range: maximum transmit power 21dBm, sensitivity -98dBm, capable of penetrating one more wall"

#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/TG/tg_12f.rst:16 c43a2f736c144b1b9011810cede2b4f5
msgid "高安全性：支持安全启动、安全调试、AES 128/192/256 加密引擎、WPA3、MD5、SHA-1/224/256、PKA（RSA/ECC）加密     引擎"
msgstr "High security: supports secure boot, secure debugging, AES 128/192/256 encryption engine, WPA3, MD5, SHA-1/224/256, PKA (RSA/ECC) encryption engine"

#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/TG/tg_12f.rst:17 3ab9a075cacd4e31b91d98fb81653754
msgid "支持 Wi-Fi 和 BLE 共存"
msgstr "Supports Wi-Fi and BLE coexistence"

